{"tid":988194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"施永青為左托市，公開叫政府放支那人才來港競爭。","createTime":"2019-01-19T23:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T02:39:27.000Z","uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"33f6ea4cc357d0ba2ec60098c5bebad197394990","tid":988194,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T23:39:19.000Z","msg":"中原集團創辦人施永青建議，如果要令香港年輕人願意到內地工作，有一些刺激的做法，「(政府)可以放內地人才來港競爭下，即刻嘗到(競爭)味道，你份工比人搶咗去，唔洗要進步?你班(香港)後生仔唔好成日咁威，香港無得做，咪返鄉下耕田囉！咁就有推力啦，你啲工畀人搶晒，你唔洗返大陸(工作)？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n托市之心昭然若揭。"},{"pid":"32367ed4fdbef4ad4b448344cc63f11c497fc188","tid":988194,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T23:43:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb05bea0243f034c3d725be861a58ead5dbc1d49","tid":988194,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T23:44:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b58db2c9ebdda838318e8cb4b4c94df1e471f659","tid":988194,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T01:35:46.000Z","msg":"咁佢地咪要放聖誕假？"},{"pid":"1ae1ae56c38d81fa5a039d494ce43a895c82c40a","tid":988194,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T01:56:05.000Z","msg":"施永清越來越鳩"},{"pid":"c8d97040df0df3e9a923833d2795d26ce8d0f913","tid":988194,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T01:58:36.000Z","msg":"點會同你番鄉下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個個做毒撚係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc818e782d94c40eb8a1913bc3d0d6e62027bbc6","tid":988194,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:01:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點會同你番鄉下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"